# ECTOR QA — known-failures allowlist.
#
# Append a row ID (one per line) to this file to ACK a known failing user story.
# Acknowledged rows are still flagged `[!]` in `docs/FEATURE_MATRIX.csv`
# (preserving the audit trail of "this used to pass") but are excluded from
# the workflow exit code in `.github/workflows/qa.yml`.
#
# Use sparingly: every entry should reference a tracking issue or be paired
# with a TODO to remove the entry once the underlying case is fixed.
#
# Example:
#   US-003   # tracked in https://github.com/jeveu/ector/issues/123
